          ዓ. ም.፡ ፓርላማን፡ ሲከፍቱ፡ ያደረጉት፡ የዙፋን፡ ንግግር።</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="am">ግርማዊ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ጥቅምት፡ ፳፫፡ ቀን፡ ፲፱፻፶፯፡ ዓ. ም.፡ ፓርላማን፡ ሲከፍቱ፡ ያደረጉት፡ የዙፋን፡ ንግግር።</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6150HaileSelassie/title/t1" xml:lang="am"/><dc:title>A Speech from Haile Selassie for the Opening of Parliament Teqemt 23, 1957 EC</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6150HaileSelassie/title/t2"/></rdf:Description><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6150HaileSelassie/person/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6150HaileSelassie"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5226haylase"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2026-04-05+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><lawd:hasName>Ḫāyla Śǝllāse I</lawd:hasName></oa:Annotation><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6150HaileSelassie/title/t1"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>ግርማዊ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ጥቅምት፡ ፳፫፡ ቀን፡ ፲፱፻፶፯፡ ዓ. ም.፡ ፓርላማን፡ ሲከፍቱ፡ ያደረጉት፡ የዙፋን፡ ንግግር።</rdfs:label></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6150HaileSelassie/title/t2"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>A Speech from Haile Selassie for the Opening of Parliament Teqemt 23, 1957 EC</rdfs:label></rdf:Description></rdf:RDF>